### Echo request
# comment line
@userId = 42
@note = hello
GET {{baseUrl}}/echo?user={{userId}}&time={{$timestamp}}
X-Env: {{envName}}
X-User: {{userId}}
X-Note: {{note}}
{{$auth.header("primary")}}

### Post text
POST {{baseUrl}}/text
Content-Type: text/plain
X-Req-Id: {{$uuid}}

hello world

### Format request
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{format}}

### Error request
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{errorPath}}
